{"tid":2331023,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"叻叻主教 #199771老屈周梓樂係意外跌死","createTime":"2020-12-18T12:39:16.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-09T13:02:33.000Z","uid":26770,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"69347c1b9feaee16bb1c812af76afb3f711ff622","tid":2331023,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:39:16.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2329514/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2329514/page/1</a><br />\n#13開始睇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外,果條叻叻主教曾經抹黑遭香港警魔強姦的女仔係性愛天使<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2269744/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2269744/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"a9d098c199b9ccc993901c8c3443840c6b2e104e","tid":2331023,"uid":79410,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"已經block咗。睇咗幾個post。五毛嚟"},{"pid":"49fe0e156b2bcaa46337d2de5bf870fbbf238b76","tid":2331023,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:40:34.000Z","msg":"大家可以查google<br />\n大公網大字標題周梓樂生前是Parkour愛好者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mTaneP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mTaneP.png&h=94904cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屈警暴死者周梓樂係玩Parkour自己跌死係黨報最高指示<br />\n<br />\n港共派左成team pr向呢個方向spin"},{"pid":"fea4c8a5bf8b261ff2761e7b42fd779792f9449f","tid":2331023,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:41:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲蓝由最鍾意咁講"},{"pid":"fe5d7ae1d82c57fcc8bbed42e1b5c675b81c7601","tid":2331023,"uid":52006,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:45:33.000Z","msg":"一早block撚左呢隻5毛狗"},{"pid":"dd2bd0f60b6a594d70801d4c8c3f6c21c0687ac4","tid":2331023,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci