class=\"red\"><span class=\"small\">* 推薦使用更安全的 Firefox 瀏覽器</span></span></em><br />\n\t<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZdCwSLv44U0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DZdCwSLv44U0&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=3dd03d51\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZdCwSLv44U0</a><br />\n\t<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"pink\"><em><span class=\"small\">最近更新日期：2020/12/28 21:21:33</span></em></span>"},{"pid":"7d0d1d040bed7839e910ad347292c69a47c48bbd","tid":2331023,"uid":237562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T01:37:01.000Z","msg":"Bam 9佢啦"},{"pid":"988a2106aaad2679448993d2215a77e916c68de7","tid":2331023,"uid":8768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T02:56:00.000Z","msg":"blocked<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b2a9514f5042197b23297a7ecb7222e2642732d","tid":2331023,"uid":199771,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>本人立論 根據事實 不服來辯<br />\n<br />\n政府化驗師 排除周梓樂遭人襲擊的可能 </strong><br />\n<br />\n政府化驗師分析尚德邨停車場的閉路電視，推測由梓樂走上停車場3樓直至他墮樓之間僅得8秒......不足以讓人向梓樂施襲後，再將他舉高拋下樓，故可排除他是遭人襲擊的可能。<br />\n<br />\n相反，若梓樂維持行上3樓時的步速，估計他有可能是「自己行埋去果度」。<br />\n<br />\n梓樂一直在2樓高層徘徊，又曾跨過石壆到行人道<br />\n<br />\n閃光是梓樂墮樓時所造成，並解釋因物件的墮下速度很快，加上深色衣物與深夜背景相若，使該物件難以被拍攝，但因石壆的外牆裝有光管，當物件快速經過光源時，便會產生一瞬間閃光現象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201228/mobile/bkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201228%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c44afd3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201228/mobile/bkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"f206d38dd5fddcdbb1f743b726568033d4d4585d","tid":2331023,"uid":304306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:03:16.000Z","msg":"嗰啲成日乜都話陰謀論嘅賤種咪又同呢條撚樣差唔多level <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3885632d715a8b25daedbada7c1c356124bd8adc","tid":2331023,"uid":199771,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"1b2a9514f5042197b23297a7ecb7222e2642732d","tid":2331023,"uid":199771,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:01:40.000Z","msg":"<strong>本人立論 根據事實 不服來辯<br />\n<br />\n政府化驗師 排除周梓樂遭人襲擊的可能 </strong><br />\n<br />\n政府化驗師分析尚德邨停車場的閉路電視，推測由梓樂走上停車場3樓直至他墮樓之間僅得8秒......不足以讓人向梓樂施襲後，再將他舉高拋下樓，故可排除他是遭人襲擊的可能。<br />\n<br />\n相反，若梓樂維持行上3樓時的步速，估計他有可能是「自己行埋去果度」。<br />\n<br />\n梓樂一直在2樓高層徘徊，又曾跨過石壆到行人道<br />\n<br />\n閃光是梓樂墮樓時所造成，並解釋因物件的墮下速度很快，加上深色衣物與深夜背景相若，使該物件難以被拍攝，但因石壆的外牆裝有光管，當物件快速經過光源時，便會產生一瞬間閃光現象。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201228/mobile/bkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20201228%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=c44afd3f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20201228/mobile/bkn-20201228173236880-1228_00822_001.html</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-29T03:04:11.000Z","msg":"專家證人、政府高級化驗師鄭郁棋調查尚德停車場時，指2樓大部分矮牆0.9米高，矮牆之後有行人道。他形容，2樓及3樓的整體設計相似，但3樓的矮牆1.2米高，矮牆之後中空。他又指，由3樓矮牆位置至2樓行人路，垂直距離4.3米。鄭郁棋表示，周梓樂身高1.75米，曾以一名1.78米的同事協助測量，在3樓距離矮牆0.8米遠，才能察覺到矮牆外是中空。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567420-20201228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567420-20201228.htm&d=FaFb5890SAgm9tgOvLsHBb2U0TaxigNo3Nw2L1ZdNcs%3D&h=cd017c02\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567420-20201228.htm&h=df605f4b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rt